title: Bosses forced Danny Dyer to take EastEnders break after months of violent mood-swings on set with cast complaining he ‘walks around like he owns Albert Square’
text:
TV Magazine 'I’m God here' Bosses forced Danny Dyer to take EastEnders break after months of violent mood-swings on set with cast complaining he ‘walks around like he owns Albert Square’ 
The hard-partying actor spoke to crew 'as if they were nothing' and would brag of his status, telling them 'you just do the lighting' Exclusive
